      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" mid="6"><![CDATA[<html> (Ask him to think a bit more.) </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html> (Ask him about the Hound.) </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html> (Ask about his family.) </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html> (Ask about his men.) </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>Do you want to know about the white aurora I always talk about? It’s scary thing. I don’t want to talk about it! <FONT color=#7e12d2>(I don’t think he is ready to talk about it)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>No! I don’t want to talk about it! Go away! <FONT color=#7e12d2>(It will be difficult to talk to him anymore)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>
The hound in my head has a jaw strong as hard steel. But it has a warm heart. He is so kind that he can kill a opponent with one bite. Hahaha. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>
Family? I did have a family, a nagging mother and 12 brothers and sisters. We were so poor that each one of us had to work. So I left my family at 10 years old and started working on the ship. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>
My men were selfish and out of control. Just like pirates. I treated them with respect and they treated me with respect. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Ropi recalls those good old memories.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
